# TextUtilsSohaib

A simple utility package for text manipulation tasks like:

- Convert to uppercase
- Convert to lowercase
- Reverse text
- Capitalize words
- Remove whitespace
- Word count
- Replace spaces with underscores

## Installation

```bash
pip install textutilsSohaib
```
